  "TCRN Design System is the shared presentation, accessibility, copy-state, and Storybook contract surface for TCRN product frontends.": { "zh-CN": "TCRN 设计系统是 TCRN 产品前端共享的展示、可访问性、文案状态和 Storybook 契约界面。", en: "TCRN Design System is the shared presentation, accessibility, copy-state, and Storybook contract surface for TCRN product frontends.", ja: "TCRN デザインシステムは、TCRN 製品フロントエンドの共有プレゼンテーション、アクセシビリティ、コピー状態、Storybook 契約サーフェスです。", ko: "TCRN 디자인 시스템은 TCRN 제품 프런트엔드의 공유 표현, 접근성, 카피 상태, Storybook 계약 표면입니다.", fr: "Le Design System TCRN est la surface contractuelle partagée pour la présentation, l'accessibilité, l'état de copie et Storybook des frontends produit TCRN." },
  "Start here": { "zh-CN": "从这里开始", en: "Start here", ja: "ここから開始", ko: "여기서 시작", fr: "Commencer ici" },
  "Use this Storybook as the contract map for shared TCRN frontend presentation. It explains which UI decisions are owned by the design system, which proof is local, and where product adoption must be proven separately.": { "zh-CN": "将此 Storybook 作为 TCRN 共享前端展示的契约地图。它说明哪些 UI 决策由设计系统负责、哪些证明仅限本地，以及产品采用必须在哪里另行证明。", en: "Use this Storybook as the contract map for shared TCRN frontend presentation. It explains which UI decisions are owned by the design system, which proof is local, and where product adoption must be proven separately.", ja: "この Storybook を TCRN 共有フロントエンド表現の契約マップとして使用します。どの UI 判断をデザインシステムが所有し、どの証明がローカル限定で、製品採用をどこで別途証明する必要があるかを示します。", ko: "이 Storybook을 TCRN 공유 프런트엔드 표현의 계약 지도로 사용합니다. 어떤 UI 결정이 디자인 시스템 소유인지, 어떤 증명이 로컬 한정인지, 제품 채택을 어디에서 별도로 증명해야 하는지 설명합니다.", fr: "Utiliser ce Storybook comme carte contractuelle de la présentation frontend partagée TCRN. Il explique quelles décisions UI appartiennent au design system, quelles preuves sont locales et où l'adoption produit doit être prouvée séparément." },
