  "Multi-navigation shell selection contracts for dense operations products, knowledge bases, and focused tools.": { "zh-CN": "面向密集运营型产品、知识库和专注型工具的多导航外壳选择契约。", en: "Multi-navigation shell selection contracts for dense operations products, knowledge bases, and focused tools.", ja: "高密度なオペレーション製品、ナレッジベース、フォーカスツール向けのマルチナビゲーションシェル選択契約。", ko: "고밀도 운영 제품, 지식 베이스, 집중형 도구를 위한 다중 내비게이션 셸 선택 계약.", fr: "Contrats de sélection de shell multi-navigation pour les produits d'exploitation denses, les bases de connaissances et les outils ciblés." },
