  "Neutral advisory: no proof route is required for this note.": { "zh-CN": "中性提示：此说明不需要证据路由。", en: "Neutral advisory: no proof route is required for this note.", ja: "中立的なアドバイザリ：このメモに証明ルートは不要です。", ko: "중립 권고: 이 메모에는 증거 경로가 필요하지 않습니다.", fr: "Avis neutre : aucune route de preuve n'est requise pour cette note." },
