  "Package-backed Knowledge Management components for static knowledge bases, document canvases, tables of contents, comments, attachments, labels, and version history.": { "zh-CN": "用于静态知识库、文档画布、目录、评论、附件、标签和版本历史的包支持知识管理组件。", en: "Package-backed Knowledge Management components for static knowledge bases, document canvases, tables of contents, comments, attachments, labels, and version history.", ja: "静的ナレッジベース、ドキュメントキャンバス、目次、コメント、添付、ラベル、バージョン履歴向けの package-backed Knowledge Management コンポーネント。", ko: "정적 지식 베이스, 문서 캔버스, 목차, 댓글, 첨부, 레이블, 버전 기록을 위한 package-backed Knowledge Management 컴포넌트.", fr: "Composants Knowledge Management package-backed pour bases de connaissances statiques, canevas de document, tables des matières, commentaires, pièces jointes, libellés et historique de version." },
